KPI Cards

Four headline metrics summarize overall performance at a glance: 
₹655K in total sales, ₹106K in total profit, 498 orders, and 3K units sold — giving management an immediate pulse on the business before drilling into detail.

Region & Category Slicers

Interactive filters let users narrow the entire dashboard down to specific regions or product categories, turning a static summary into a self-service exploration tool.

Order Date Range Slider

A date range selector (currently set to 26-01-2023 to 31-12-2023) lets users zoom into any custom time window to analyze performance for a specific period rather than the full year.

Pie Chart — Sum of Sales by Category and Region

Breaks down the ₹655K in total sales across Technology, Office Supplies, and Furniture, split further by region within each slice — showing not just which category sells best, but where.

Bar Chart — Sum of Profit by Region

Ranks regions by profit contribution.
West leads with roughly ₹40K+ in profit, followed by South, with the East region(s) trailing — highlighting where the business is most profitable versus where margins are weaker.

Area Chart — Sum of Sales and Sum of Profit by Month

Tracks sales and profit trends across all 12 months, with visible peaks around mid-year and again toward September–October, helping identify seasonal demand patterns for planning purposes.


